    <Title/Known Bugs/
    <Abstract>
    This documents summarizes known bugs in Mozart. New bugs can be
    reported by sending email to <REF.EXTERN
    TO="mailto:bugs@mozart-oz.org">bugs@mozart-oz.org</REF.EXTERN> or
    via our bug tracking system reachable under <REF.EXTERN
    TO="http://www.mozart-oz.org/cgi-bin/oz-bugs">http://www.mozart-oz.org/cgi-bin/oz-bugs</REF.EXTERN>.
    This URL is also a good starting point to find out more about
    already known bugs (fixed and unfixed ones). However it is
    intended to be used primarily by the developpers and also
    documents the state of the system currently being under
    development, so it might list bugs that do not appear in the
    released system and vice versa.
    </Abstract>
